XiVO data access object

Dependencies:
-------------

needs mock version >= 1.0
lib-python (xivo-skaro)
sqlalchemy >= 0.6.3
postgresql


To Run Unittests:
-------------------

- Install PostgreSQL
- Create a database asterisktest
- Create a user asterisk / password asterisk
        create DATABASE asterisktest;
        create USER asterisk with password 'asterisk';
        grant all ON DATABASE asterisktest to asterisk;

PYTHONPATH=</path/to/lib-python> nosetests
